36:16.960 --> 36:18.160
What?

36:22.720 --> 36:23.960
That's wrong.

36:23.960 --> 36:25.720
What do you mean?

36:25.720 --> 36:30.440
There's a hidden song
deep inside her soul.

36:30.440 --> 36:31.880
- What is it?

36:33.960 --> 36:35.480
What?

36:36.440 --> 36:38.040
Ruby.

36:44.160 --> 36:46.080
What is this?

36:47.080 --> 36:48.640
Christmas.

36:49.360 --> 36:51.760
